Using `frontend-design` to build a distinctive developer tools hero.

**Direction:** Industrial terminal — dark near-black canvas, electric amber accent, hard-edged brutalist CTA, dot-grid atmosphere. Syne for display type, JetBrains Mono for code. The code preview types itself in. No pill buttons, no purple gradients, no safe choices.

